#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:4
msgid "Land degradation and SDG 15.3.1"
msgstr "土地退化和 SDG 15.3.1"

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:6
msgid ""
"As part of the \"2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development\", Sustainable "
"Development Goal (SDG) 15 is to:"
msgstr "作为 \"2030年可持续发展议程 \"的一部分，可持续发展目标（SDG）15是："

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:9
msgid ""
"\"Protect, restore and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems, "
"sustainably manage forests, combat desertification, and halt and reverse "
"land degradation and halt biodiversity loss\""
msgstr "\"保护、恢复和促进陆地生态系统的可持续利用，可持续地管理森林，防治荒漠化，并制止和扭转土地退化，遏制生物多样性的丧失\""

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:13
msgid ""
"Each SDG has specific targets addressing different components, in this case,"
" of life on land. Target 15.3 aims to:"
msgstr "每个可持续发展目标都有针对不同组成部分的具体目标，在本案例中是针对土地上的生活。具体目标15.3旨在："

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:16
msgid ""
"\"By 2030, combat desertification, restore degraded land and soil, including"
" land affected by desertification, drought and floods, and strive to achieve"
" a land degradation-neutral world\""
msgstr "\"截止2030年，防治荒漠化，恢复退化的土地和土壤，包括受荒漠化、干旱和洪水影响的土地，并努力实现一个土地退化中立的世界\""

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:20
msgid ""
"Indicators will be used then to assess the progress of each SDG target. In "
"the case of SDG 15.3 the progress towards a land degradation neutral world "
"will be assessed using indicator 15.3.1:"
msgstr "然后将使用指标来评估每个SDG目标的进展。就可持续发展目标15.3而言，将使用指标15.3.1评估实现土地退化中立世界的进展："

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:24
msgid "\"proportion of land that is degraded over total land area\""
msgstr "\"退化的土地占总土地面积的比例\""

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:26
msgid ""
"As the custodian agency for SDG 15.3, the United Nations Convention to "
"Combat Desertification (UNCCD) has developed a `Good Practice Guidance (GPG)"
" <https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_SDG-"
"Indicator-15.3.1_version2_2021.pdf>`_ providing recommendations on how to "
"calculate SDG Indicator 15.3.1."
msgstr ""
"作为 SDG 15.3 的负责机构，联合国防治荒漠化公约（UNCCD）制定了`良好实践指南 (GPG) "
"<https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_SDG-"
"Indicator-15.3.1_version2_2021.pdf>`_ ，提供了关于如何计算 SDG 指标 15.3.1 的建议。"

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:31
msgid ""
"This page provides a brief introduction to SDG Indicator 15.3.1 and "
"describes how each indicator is calculated by |trends.earth|."
msgstr "本页面简要介绍 SDG 指标 15.3.1，并说明 |trends.earth| 如何计算每个指标。"

