#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:1062
msgid ""
"Drought intensity classes are identified by assessing the December SPI-12 "
"values for ear year of time-series. The December SPI-12 values represent the"
" precipitation deficits (or excesses) over the Gregorian (January-December) "
"calendar year. Positive SPI values are discarded, since they indicate that "
"there was no drought in the given period."
msgstr ""
"干旱强度等级是通过评估时间序列中每一年的12月SPI-12值来确定的。12月的SPI-12值代表公历年（1-12月）的降水赤字（或过剩）。正的SPI值被放弃，因为它们表明在给定的时期内没有干旱。"

#: ../../source/for_users/features/unccdreporting.rst:1066
